{
  "name": "ChartFormat",
  "summary": "<p>如果使用的属性或方法不适用于 <strong>ChartFormat</strong> 对象所附加到的对象的类型，则会产生运行时错误。</p>\n",
  "description": "<p>提供对图表元素艺术字格式的访问。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#jsObject_Application\">Application</a></strong> 对象。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象的创建程序的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象（可对一个 OLE 自动化对象使用该属性来返回该对象的应用程序）。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>){\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}\n</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "AutoShapeType",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定形状的类型。只读 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/MsoAutoShapeType 枚举.html\">MsoAutoShapeType</a></strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 上图表的第一个数据系列的第一个数据标签的形状是否为 msoShapeRectangle。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">DataLabels</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoShapeType</span> == msoShapeRectangle)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例判断工作表 Sheet1 上第一张图表的第二个数据系列的第一个数据标签的形状是否为 msoShapeOval，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">DataLabels</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoShapeType</span> == msoShapeOval) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据标签的形状是 msoShapeOval&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;数据标签的形状不是 msoShapeOval&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoAutoShapeType",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Fill",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个包含图表元素填充格式属性的父图表元素的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FillFormat/FillFormat .htm#jsObject_FillFormat\">FillFormat</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置图表工作表 Chart1 图表区的颜色为黄色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示工作表 Sheet1 中第一个内嵌图表区的填充渐变样式是否为混合的。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">GradientStyle</span> == msoGradientMixed)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "FillFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Glow",
      "summary": "<p>发光效果为图形添加了色彩鲜明的彩色边缘。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个包含图表元素发光格式属性的指定图表的 <strong>GlowFormat</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 图表区发光的透明度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Glow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Transparency</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置工作表 Sheet1 中第一个内嵌图表区的发光效果的半径值为 1 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Glow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Radius</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "GlowFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Line",
      "summary": "<p>对于线条来说，<strong>LineFormat</strong> 对象代表线条本身；而对于带有边框的图表来说，<strong>LineFormat</strong> 对象代表边框。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个包含指定图表元素线条格式属性的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接���/表格 API 参考/LineFormat/LineFormat .htm#jsObject_LineFormat\">LineFormat</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置工作表 Sheet1 中第一个内嵌图表区的线条粗细为 1.6 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1.6</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 图表区线条的虚线样式是否为实线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DashStyle</span> == msoLineSolid)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "LineFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
