    {
      "name": "PictureFormat",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回包含图片的指定图表的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PictureFormat/PictureFormat .htm#jsObject_PictureFormat\">PictureFormat</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表的图表区图片亮度为 0.2 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将图表工作表 Chart1 图表区的图片转换为黑白。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> = msoPictureBlackAndWhite\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "PictureFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Shadow",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ShadowFormat/ShadowFormat .htm#jsObject_ShadowFormat\">ShadowFormat</a></strong> 对象，该对象包含图表元素的阴影格式属性。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表区的底纹的模糊度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Blur</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置图表工作表 Chart1 图表区的阴影类型。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shadow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = msoShadow8\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ShadowFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SoftEdge",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定图表的 <strong>SoftEdgeFormat</strong> 对象，该对象包含图表的柔化边缘格式设置属性。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 图表区柔化边缘效果的大小（以磅为单位）。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SoftEdge</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Radius</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表区柔化边缘效果的大小为 0.5 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SoftEdge</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Radius</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "SoftEdgeFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "TextFrame2",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个包含指定图表元素文本格式的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/TextFrame2/TextFrame2 .htm#jsObject_TextFrame2\">TextFrame2</a></strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置图表工作表 Chart1 图表区文本框中字体的大小为 10 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表区的文本框方向是否为水平方向。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Orientation</span> == msoTextOrientationHorizontal)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "TextFrame2",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "ThreeD",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ThreeDFormat/ThreeDFormat .htm#jsObject_ThreeDFormat\">ThreeDFormat</a></strong> 对象，该对象包含指定图表的三维效果格式属性。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 图表区的底部凹凸效果类型是否为 Angle 凹凸效果。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThreeD</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">BevelBottomType</span> == msoBevelAngle)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置工作表 Sheet1 第一个内嵌图表区延伸表面为线框材料。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chartformat = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ChartArea</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>\n    chartformat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThreeD</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PresetMaterial</span> = msoMaterialWireFrame\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
